item.title: About
item.description: About Weâ€™ve never had a place to belong. So together we search aimlessly. Formation (2004-2006) Zach, Max, and Mikhail all met in High School in a small town in Virginia to form Together Searching Aimlessly, a heavily electronically and classically influenced group, who have gone on to see moderate commercial success and a growing cult following. They started making music in a friends basement in 2004, and recorded many of their first songs with low-budget instruments, recording methods, and production.
